#-      Wheatistan Law§0
§0       First Edition§0
§0
§0
§0             by:§0
§0           Kinnoin
#- Foreword§0
§0
§0This lawbook is a compilation of local laws enacted via concensus on the voting board. §0
§0It is not inclusive of all laws in Wheatistan. §0
§0It does not include laws covered by the CivCraft Common Law (CCL).  As this is the first edition, it is
#- accurate to the publishing date and no further, Laws were written as interpreted from voting records at the town hall.§0
§0Votes still in progress at the date of publishing are not presented here. §0
§0Minor acts of governance are not presented here.
