#- Founding Laws:§0
§0
§0No tortue is permitted.§0
§0
§07 day public voting by default.§0
§0
§0Any land may be claimed with a mandated 1 block build-free perimeter around roads, rivers, beaches, and pre-excisting 
#- improvements or builds.
#- Government, Citizenship and Voting§0
§0
§020190809a§0
§0Any law with 3 days of unanimous vote passes, unless regarding private property (20191020a).
#- 20190809b§0
§0Any law with 7 days of no majority vote goes to town debate.§0
§0
§020191020b§0
§0Members of foreign governments cannot vote.§0
§0

#- 20191024b§0
§0Dual citizens henceforth require a vote to join Wheatistan.§0
§0
§020191024c§0
§0Dual citizens are limited to 30x30 private claims.
#- 20190902b§0
§0All posted votes must include the final date of voting.§0
§0
§020191104a§0
§0The title "Dear Leader" is henceforth bestowed upon Axusgrad.
#- 20200106a§0
§0Local voting walls may enact laws concerning local issues.§0
§0
§020200106b§0
§0Created the position of "Mayor" for small towns.
#- 20200130a§0
§0Single-Citizenship votes last 3 days.§0
§0
§020200413a§0
§0A Wheatistan-wide census will be conducted every 3 months, with inactive citizens removed.
#- Builds and Claims§0
§0
§0
§020190804a§0
§0No structures may be built over public roads.§0
§0
§020191006a§0
§0All builds must have the owner or builder's name clearly posted.
#- 20191013a§0
§0Historic buildings will be preserved.§0
§0
§020191020a§0
§0Modifications to private claims by vote require an 80% supermajority and two weeks, even if voting is unanimous.
#- 20191024c§0
§0Dual citizens are limited to 30x30 private claims.
#- Infrastructure§0
§0
§020190807a§0
§0Only Wheatistan group reinforcement on public land.§0
§0
§020190826a§0
§0Skyroads are permitted more than 200 blocks above public roads.
#- 20191006b§0
§0Roads should be named.§0
§0
§020191020b§0
§0Foreign shops in the public shopping area need to reciprocate equivalent, rent-free space in their main shopping area.§0
§0

#- 20191024a§0
§0Axusgrad and Esorscher will perform public infrastructure upgrades.§0
§0
§020191102a§0
§0Public stables shall be walled to prevent horse theft.
#- 20191111a§0
§0Automating public farms is permitted.§0
§0
§020200307§0
§0Items left in the public Blast Furance are public.
#- International Relations and Diplomacy§0
§0
§020190828a§0
§0Announce a formal military alliance with Varathia.§0
§0
§020191001a§0
§0After sufficient evidence of foreign crimes, a citizen may be extradited for trial.
#- 20191020b§0
§0Foreign shops in the public shopping area need to reciprocate equivalent, rent-free space in their main shopping area.§0
§0
§020191206a§0
§0Narwhal_19 elected ambassador to Varathia.
#- 20191210a§0
§0Join the coalition.§0
§0
§020191226b§0
§0Esorcher elected ambassador to the Coalition.§0
§0
§020200405b§0
§0Accepted joint stewardship of Wycliffe aqua nether portal.
#- Miscellaneous Laws§0
§0
§020190807a§0
§0Horse, Parrot, and wolf murder is illegal.§0
§0
§020190921a§0
§0A saddle left on a horse without the owner present may be taken.
